Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mulai, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.75,0:00:10.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip. Sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Wakatsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti yang kubilang sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,ini bukan mantra, tapi jampi-jampi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.85,0:00:25.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, belum tentu cintamu\Nakan terbalaskan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.81,0:00:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, jampi-jampi dari penyihir asli itu
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,rasanya seperti dapat berkah ilahi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi lebih berani.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga pernyataan cintamu sukses, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Terima kasih, Nico.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kabari aku kalau sudah dapat pacar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.84,0:00:42.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pacar, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Nico...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang beratmu berapa kilo?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Ke-Kenapa tanya itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggi badanmu 158 cm, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai orang yang mengawasi kesehatanmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku perlu tahu berat badanmu juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.71,0:02:45.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.35,0:02:49.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, Moi. Jangan tanya\Nberat badan anak perempuan, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang, demi kesehatan...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masalahnya bukan itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi ini benar-benar tidak pekaan\Npada perasaan anak gadis!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.21,0:03:01.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata ini topik\Nyang sangat sensitif untuk anak gadis.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku akan lebih berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.31,0:03:05.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia keren banget, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ganteng banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk saat ini, baru sedikit yang sadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,jumlahnya bertambah\Nsecara perlahan tapi pasti,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan juga mulai membuat hatiku gelisah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,mulai populer.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi memang ada masalah besar, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.77,0:03:36.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku siap.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu bisa tangkap tanpa melihat?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama aku bisa bayangkan bentuk objeknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa mendeteksi lewat samar bunyi,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,aroma, dan gerakan dalam angin.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini latihan untuk mempertajam indra\Nselain penglihatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu tidak latihan\Nmempertajam hal lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.05,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Rasanya enak sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.66,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku agak kepo soal sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua berpacaran, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.38,0:04:19.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang lihat sekilas saja\Nbisa langsung tahu perasaanmu, tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.95,0:04:24.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar?\NTapi Moi masih belum sadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, orang satu itu\Nmemang lain dari yang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.15,0:04:32.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tinggal serumah dengan Nico,\Ntapi tidak pernah ada kemajuan, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidur dan bangun di waktu yang sama,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.51,0:04:39.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu diam sambil minum kopi, lo.\NOgre macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya itu aneh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagiku, Nico-lah yang melewatkan kesempatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.37,0:04:48.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu memang imut, tapi kerjaannya\Nbengong dan tidak ada inisiatif.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan, tolong lebih rinci lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya, harus PDKT dengan lebih frontal...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biarkan kilau rambut\Nmenuturkan pesona femininmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iklan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rambut lembut bak sutra\Nyang melambai diembus angin.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Operasinya dimulai saat istirahat siang, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.71,0:05:08.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuai obrolan kita kemarin malam.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Morihito selalu pergi ke gedung timur\Nyang ada mesin penjual otomatisnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koridor penghubung itulah kesempatan kita!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rencana mereka berdua adalah,\N"Membuat Nico terlihat cantik
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan mengembuskan angin ke rambutnya."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.02,0:05:25.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat Morihito menyeberang dari gedung barat\Nlewat koridor penghubung,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kanshi yang berada di taman
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.46,0:05:30.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan mengembuskan angin ke arah Nico\Ndan membuat rambutnya melambai.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga beruntung!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, jam istirahat siang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi sudah tiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan, sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kirimkan anginnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sinyalnya. Ayo mulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senkouran!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya ada angin, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus. Kerja bagus, Nico!\NKamu cantik banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intip.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matanya gelap banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tidak bekerja.\NReaksinya masih nol, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita butuh angin lagi\Nuntuk menggerakkan hatinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tambahkan anginnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Angin yang lebih kuat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.91,0:06:28.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja. Anginnya pasti masih kurang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sip. Nico, akan kutiupkan\Nlebih banyak angin untukmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini? Anginnya tiba-tiba...\Ntidak ada angin?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.30,0:06:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini?\NKenapa tidak ada angin ke arahku?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo, Moi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu kenapa, sih?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Nico sudah terlihat cantik?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Kamu ngomong apa barusan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Bu Guru ruang UKS.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.71,0:07:03.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku sudah cantik?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu stres karena sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo?\NAnginnya hanya bertiup di sekitar sini...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rekap Data Pengukuran Badan-nya!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu rekap milik para siswi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak lihat satu lembar pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren parah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otogi dari kelas 1-3.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.58,0:07:40.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malah membuatnya makin populer.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu, mereka dimarahi habis-habisan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Membuat rambutmu melambai\Nsupaya hatiku tergerak?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan kebiasaan asbun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Otogi. Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enak, ya. Moi jadi populer\Nkarena melakukan hal hebat tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak juga, ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak senang?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, aku senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.41,0:08:07.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa canggung\Nkarena tiba-tiba disapa orang asing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisnya, selama ini temanku sedikit\Nkarena sibuk berlatih.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi, Wakatsuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ada waktu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada siswa yang mengundangmu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, namanya Ishii.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bertanya,\Napa aku ada waktu saat piknik nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gusti! Itu dia mau menembakmu, tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin, lah. Aku tidak kenal dia, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya ampun, anak ini tidak paham apa-apa!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.94,0:08:55.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar, ya. Gadis penyihir Nico itu\Npopuler banget di sekolah kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa pakai sihir,\Npribadi yang ceria dan ramah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah begitu, kamu imut!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Imutnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kara, kamu mabuk?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih, kalau saat piknik,\Nberarti ke sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.65,0:09:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikon SMA Asunaro, Pohon Ara Gunung Futatsu\Nyang selalu mekar di luar musim!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak paham. Kuku, bisa bantu jelaskan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di tempat kita piknik, Gunung Futatsu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada sebuah pohon yang populer\Nsebagai "Pohon Perjodohan".
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada legenda yang mengatakan\Nkalau dua muda-mudi
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.18,0:09:24.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,membuat janji dan makan siang bersama\Ndi bawah pohon itu akan berjodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pohon Perjodohan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya, itu tempat yang bagus\Nuntuk menembak. Tidak penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak penting...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.58,0:09:40.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kara juga mau jatuh cinta, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu bisa jadi tempat yang cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tembak saja si Morihito itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di hari piknik? Ke Moi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa, tidak bisa,\Ntidak bisa, tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya kamu Dio?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu selalu menyemangati cinta orang lain,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.75,0:09:58.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi tidak mau mewujudkan cintamu sendiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico bukan gadis\Nyang bisa menarik perhatian Moi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.18,0:10:08.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu mengacaukan sesuatu.\NDia pasti melihatku sebagai adik.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku ingin fokus latihan dulu sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak punya waktu untuk cinta-cintaan\Nsebelum menjadi penyihir yang ahli.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan ekskul!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhenti bersikap sok keren, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan tertipu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan cari alasan seperti,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku mau sibuk jadi atlet,\Ntidak ada waktu pacaran"!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu namanya kabur!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku takut menembak Moi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan, tolong aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.70,0:10:35.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari itu, aku paham betul\Nkalau Moi tidak tertarik padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menggodanya,\Ntapi matanya hitam banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.84,0:10:42.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico belum pernah melihat\Nmata hitam sekelam itu sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.32,0:10:46.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, aku pernah mengangkat topik ini\Npada Morihito.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, dia jawab...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ini Roh Pendamping.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita berkewajiban mengawal Nico.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mencampur emosi pribadi pada target\Nhanya akan memperkeruh misi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matanya hitam kelam.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapan kamu menanyakan hal seperti itu?\NKan, jangan, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.37,0:11:02.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mentalnya orang itu sekeras baja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum ditambah wataknya yang tekun itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia sangat berkomitmen
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.13,0:11:10.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan merasa tidak boleh melihat Nico\Nsebagai target romansa.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.25,0:11:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku yakin kamu lebih spesial\Ndari orang lain untuknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu hanya sebagai roh pendamping, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.11,0:11:18.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin, dia masih belum sadar
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.02,0:11:24.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau sudah menyembunyikan\Nemosi aslinya di balik komitmen.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, mari buat dia goyah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak,\Nikuti ritme sendiri saat mendaki, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak usah buru-buru.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika mendaki dengan kecepatan sendiri,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,kamu bisa melihat\Npemandangan indah di sekitar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Guru ngomong apa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.67,0:11:48.10,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kayaknya dia bermaksud menyemangati, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak paham sama sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.35,0:11:52.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Guru, itu dialog populer\NKapten Fuwa dari U.M, lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi, kita mendaki sambil ngobrol, yuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang mengundangmu ke Pohon Perjodohan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ekspresinya masih sulit dibaca.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia sudah mulai goyah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan mengawalmu saat di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan jaga jarak,\Nkamu bebas melakukan apa saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudku bukan itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.61,0:12:27.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi tidak keberatan\Nkalau ada yang menembak Nico?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Nico punya pacar?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar baik-baik, Nico.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.18,0:12:41.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico bisa menikmati\Nkehidupan sehari-hari dan SMA
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,sebagai siswi SMA biasa, bukan penyihir.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico menikmati kehidupan SMA-ku, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.80,0:12:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico bukan lagi gadis\Nyang dirundung seperti saat kecil dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sasaran tembak?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanda tentara angkatan udara, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tanda yang aku pakai ini
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,sebenarnya logo sebuah band.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.78,0:13:36.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin kamu tidak kenal,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi ini logo band besar\Nyang setara Beatles
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan The Rolling Stones\Ndalam sejarah musik rock.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.34,0:13:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sebenarnya, aku lebih penasaran\Npada film yang diadaptasi dari opera rock
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.81,0:13:47.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,autobiografi karangan gitarisnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.38,0:13:51.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu karya penting dalam subkultur Mod.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.58,0:13:55.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kamu kelihatan\Nseperti penggemar Rockers.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.30,0:14:00.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sempat mengelilingi\Nbanyak toko pakaian antik
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk mencari parka model ekor ikan M51.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.35,0:14:07.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Otogi Morihito.\NKita teman sekelas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Magami Keigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sering siaran langsung\Nuntuk ngobrol soal subkultur.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sempat, coba tonton, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita makan di sana, yuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otogi, kamu ada waktu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ehm, Pohon Perjodohan-nya\Ndi sekitar sini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.81,0:14:39.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus menolak Ishii dengan sopan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, ramai banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi ngeri sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang yang sedang kasmaran\Nke sini semua!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya seperti tersesat\Nke tempat yang tidak pantas!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pemandangan yang mirip\Ngerbang kedatangan di bandara.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus mencari Ishii.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wakatsuki, sebelah sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, ketemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, kamu jadi repot-repot ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok jadi banyak, sih?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini?\NIshii, kenapa ada rombongan sebesar ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.91,0:15:09.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf. Mereka ramai datang\Nsaat aku bilang sedang menunggumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang ingin menembak Nico\Nada sebanyak ini...?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong berikan jampi-jampi cinta pada kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.13,0:15:16.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata bukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malu-maluin!\NJampi-jampi yang itu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa harus di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.75,0:15:24.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisnya, berkahnya pasti berlipat\Nkalau dilakukan di bawah pohon itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.11,0:15:24.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak akan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak benar.\NSiapa yang menyebarkan rumor ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pohon ini tidak ada hubungannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dengar, cinta kami pasti terbalaskan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya, sihirmu bisa membuatku ganteng!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya, aku akan dapat calon istri\Nyang kembar lima!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rumornya makin aneh\Nkarena ditambah macam-macam!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa bertanggung jawab!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.25,0:15:41.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kabur!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.91,0:15:43.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tunggu!\N- Kumohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa, tidak bisa,\Ntidak bisa, tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus sembunyi. Kecil Mungil!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo? Dia menghilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pergi ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus kabur sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Duh, capeknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin makan siang bersama Moi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, aku masuk ke saku siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ada perlu apa\Nsampai mengajakku ke sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.41,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dia sedang bicara dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak gadis. Gadis yang sedang grogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan, ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu mau berkencan denganku?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi sedang ditembak!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan menjawab apa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak kenal kamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.71,0:16:42.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku pernah melihatmu di stasiun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu menolong seorang nenek.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hargai perasaanmu padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.21,0:16:53.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku tidak bisa membalas perasaanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku tidak mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa jawabannya sudah jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.05,0:17:03.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia frontal banget, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu akan melukainya, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu keren banget\Nkarena jawab dengan frontal.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia malah makin naksir, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otogi, kamu tidak punya pacar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.29,0:17:12.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada orang yang kamu taksir?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang aku taksir, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.91,0:17:26.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada, sih...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku punya seseorang yang spesial.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin kamu lebih spesial\Ndari orang lain untuknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia orangnya suka bikin cemas,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan selalu mengandalkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mau membuatnya kecewa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah sibuk memenuhi tanggung jawab itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang spesial?\NApa bedanya dengan menaksir?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak pernah pikirkan ke sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak perlu pikirkan dengan rumit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba bayangkan orang itu sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu tidak pernah jatuh cinta padanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Momen aku jatuh cinta...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico punya momen itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang merundungmu lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.81,0:18:36.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan. Ayahku pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.60,0:18:40.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah dan Ibu memang jarang akur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.45,0:18:45.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya, membangun keluarga antara\Npenyihir dan manusia biasa itu memang sulit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa terjadi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.38,0:18:58.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatan sihir Nico\Ntiba-tiba meluap dan meledak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.98,0:19:03.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatan ini akan membuatku makin dibenci.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sayang Ayah,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku masih ingin digendong Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga kuat, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Moi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya momen itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lapar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku makan bekal sendiri saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sihirnya hampir terlepas!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar lagi.\NBahaya kalau terlepas di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.11,0:20:03.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kabur seperti lalat!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, duh. Aku terdorong kembali!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nico?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.61,0:20:30.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang latihan sihir sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Moi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak berat?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.98,0:20:46.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, soalnya aku kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak nakal, jangan memanjat pohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.20,0:20:58.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau memanjat ke tempat tinggi,\Nmaka kejarlah impianmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dihampiri kakek yang aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siswa yang sedang piknik?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.25,0:21:06.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kamu di sini?\NPadahal yang lain makan bekal di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.25,0:21:10.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada. Habisnya,\Ndi sana ada Pohon Perjodohan yang terkenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.34,0:21:12.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kesal karena banyak orang pacaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.55,0:21:16.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Legenda dan rumor itu memang cepat berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang ini mulai mengoceh sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena bentuknya bagus,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.15,0:21:25.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang-orang mulai menyebut\NPohon Ara besar itu Pohon Perjodohan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aslinya bukan pohon itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.05,0:21:31.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kakek tua sepertimu\Ntahu rumor anak-anak muda?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.51,0:21:34.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Joji, kamu di sini, ya. Waktunya pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.94,0:21:41.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Legenda sebenarnya, muda-mudi\Nyang makan bekal di Pohon Konara sederhana
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,sebelah sana yang akan jadian.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.41,0:21:46.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisnya, kami generasi pertama\Nyang menyebarkan rumor itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak salah lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.50,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Jadi ingat dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pohon sederhana sebelah sana?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.78,0:21:54.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kanshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu lihat Nico?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menghilang entah ke mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, dia tidak pergi ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ke sana saja, yuk. Makan bekal di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu mau menembakku, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.12,0:22:05.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ngawur!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.35,0:22:07.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.21,0:22:09.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,legenda itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.81,0:24:01.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu-satunya cara buat Moi\Nmenoleh padaku adalah dengan hipnotis!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.45,0:24:02.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hipnotis?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan, lihat koin 5 yen ini baik-baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu akan menaksir Nico,\Nkamu akan menaksir Nico.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.45,0:24:09.30,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Nico cinta diri sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.31,0:24:10.43,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Nico imut banget!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.43,0:24:11.74,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu yang kena?!
